Package: bis557
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of Ridge Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person(“Yueyi”, “Li”, email = “yueyi.li@yale.edu”,
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Yueyi Li <yueyi.li@yale.edu>
Description: An implementation of linear model in R with Ridge regulation. It takes an 		input data frame (X), a response vector (y) and a vector of tuning parameter 		lambda. Can calculate the optimized value of the tuning parameter and the 		coefficients of the fitted penalized linear model. 
